OL,7,FTributes have been paid to two
OL,8,Fpensioners who died in a car crash
OL,9,Fwhich happened near Barry on Saturday
OL,10,F2 November.
OL,12,FThe women have been named as Madeline
OL,13,FElaine Brooks, 85, and Beverley
OL,14,FPugsley, 69. South Wales Police say
OL,15,Fthat two men, aged 24 and 67, remain
OL,16,Fin hospital.
OL,18,FBoth families of Madeline and Beverley
OL,19,Fhave been remembering them fondly.
