OL,7,F"Madeline Elaine Brooks, a mother,
OL,8,Fnanna, great grandmother & aunt who
OL,9,Fwas born in Penarth and lived in Barry
OL,10,Ffor over 65 years.
OL,12,F"Madeline was a lively lady, full of
OL,13,Fenergy."
OL,15,F"She loved Ballroom dancing and was a
OL,16,Fteacher at many venues around Wales,
OL,17,Fstill attending afternoon dances in
OL,18,Fher later years.
