OL,7,F"Beverley was a quiet lady who loved
OL,8,Fher job, having worked for the BBC for
OL,9,Fbiggest part of her life in various
OL,10,Froles and in the later as a Researcher
OL,11,Ffor many television programmes. She
OL,12,Fwas still partly working after
OL,13,Fretirement."
OL,15,FSouth Wales Police is continuing to
OL,16,Fappeal for anyone with information
OL,17,Fconcerning the collision or anyone
OL,18,Fwith dashcam footage to come forward.
