OL,7,FSenior investigating officer, Sergeant
OL,8,FGareth Jones-Roberts, said: "We are
OL,9,Fappealing to anybody who was driving
OL,10,Fin the area between 1.30pm and 1.50pm
OL,11,Fon Saturday afternoon and who may have
OL,12,Fany information that can assist this
OL,13,Finvestigation to get in touch with us.
OL,15,F"If you have dash-cam in your
OL,16,Fvehicles, please contact us. We are
OL,17,Fparticularly keen to hear from anyone
OL,18,Fwho can give us extra detail on the
OL,19,Fmanner of driving of a grey Audi RS 4
OL,20,Fprior to the collision."
